{"tid":1840913,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[醫護罷工］其實有兩全其美方法，推呢個","createTime":"2020-01-25T05:11:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T07:27:19.000Z","uid":264970,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ea4853833cbb0ab3d5972db79cc54043a7e88fc5","tid":1840913,"uid":264970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T05:11:30.000Z","msg":"知道有好多醫護擔心罷工會影響病人，其實有個方法可以平衡到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日病房姑娘開始拒絕收症，令所有case逼晒係A&amp;E</span></span><br />\n<br />\n病房姑娘HCA落去<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">A&amp;E幫手</span></span><br />\n<br />\n醫護照返工照顧病人，不過係A&amp;E做<br />\n<br />\n一逼爆，膠層就驚爆傳染<br />\n<br />\n唔駛一日政府就可以跪低<br />\n<br />\n當然醫護要做足保護措施<br />\n<br />\n利申：RN試過係美國咁樣罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc6c85d09f3d4f672519deacf4a8819fd023ea34","tid":1840913,"uid":264970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T05:12:37.000Z","msg":"自推1"},{"pid":"6bdf62fbaaaa83a1b7ce0434b36ac49115913aa6","tid":1840913,"uid":264970,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T05:12:56.000Z","msg":"自推2"},{"pid":"eb5d7d0cefddbfd03d63e04197f7ca81bcd6b855","tid":1840913,"uid":264970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T05:13:09.000Z","msg":"自推3"},{"pid":"dfbe793393abffd6f990b26f832d5cbc7e8c8642","tid":1840913,"uid":264970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T05:24:21.000Z","msg":"自推4"},{"pid":"1c7ea6eb3bb60fa767326e247b4ec95ae2d207a7","tid":1840913,"uid":264970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T05:24:35.000Z","msg":"自推5"},{"pid":"74fd091deac42084e839b475a1cd9c64ec3674f8","tid":1840913,"uid":264970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T05:24:49.000Z","msg":"自推6"},{"pid":"ad956f94a1d923799e36c0d2ad61e883a7fb581e